# 3D Scrolling Website — Group of Companies

A visually stunning, scroll-driven 3D website showcasing a fictional conglomerate ("Nexus Group") and its subsidiary companies. Built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript using Three.js for 3D rendering and GSAP ScrollTrigger for scroll-driven animations.

## Proposed Changes

### Project: `/Users/erangasenadeera/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/nexus-group/`

---

#### [NEW] index.html
Full semantic HTML structure:
- Sticky nav bar with glassmorphism
- Hero section: Three.js canvas background with floating 3D geometric logo
- "About" section: company overview + animated stat counters
- "Our Companies" section: horizontal 3D card carousel (6 subsidiary companies with icons)
- "Services" section: 3D icon grid with hover animations
- "Global Presence" section: animated world map dots
- Footer with links

#### [NEW] index.css
- CSS custom properties design system (colors, spacing, typography)
- Dark futuristic theme (deep navy/black + electric blue/violet gradients)
- Glassmorphism cards
- Scroll-reveal animations
- Responsive layout

#### [NEW] main.js
- Three.js: animated 3D particle starfield background, rotating geometric logo
- GSAP + ScrollTrigger: section reveals, horizontal card scroll, text animations
- Intersection Observer fallback for scroll effects
- Counter animation for stats

